</div>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="_provisioning_plugins">1.5. Provisioning plugins</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Now you will provision the plugins in <strong>Productive</strong> in order to apply the changes. The filters will be available in the <strong>search</strong> and in the <strong>category view</strong>.</p>
</div>
