<h3 id="_deploying_the_plugins">2.3. Deploying the plugins</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Deploy the plugins in <strong>Productive</strong> to save the changes and display the Order property in the <strong>Item view</strong> and the <strong>Shopping cart</strong>.</p>
